data.description: ASSUMABLE VA LOAN at 4.75% by a Veteran or Active Military.  Walk to downtown Clayton! The SYCAMORE PLAN was a Bronze winner in the 2023 Parade of Homes! Come take a look at this gorgeous 3-bedroom ranch home at The Walk in East Village, a 55+ community! Large covered front porch for mingling with your neighbors.  Tons of upgrades including: Custom lighting, LVP throughout (no carpet), family room with trey ceiling, crown molding, gas fireplace, built-ins and ceiling fan.  Kitchen features gorgeous navy lower cabinets and island with quartz countertops, stainless appliance, gas range and pendant lighting.  All bedrooms have crown molding.   Spacious primary bedroom with huge walk-in closet, primary bath has zero entry shower & frameless door.  Open floor plan great for entertaining! Screened porch, patio and fenced backyard. Neighborhood features pickleball, pool, gym, putting green, billiards room, craft room, yoga room, sidewalks and greenway trail.  HOA includes yard maintenance.
